data.description: !!!MOTIVATED SELLER!!!RAPID CLOSE AVAILABLE!!! Looking to be in your next dream home before the first of the year? Look no further than this 3,000 square foot traditional home that has so much to offer! Nestled in a prime location and bordered by a greenbelt, this home offers you additional privacy and no backyard neighbors. The chef's inspired kitchen is adorned with granite countertops, built-in stainless steel appliances, and an oversized island that makes food preparation or hosting gatherings a breeze. Opening up to the main living room and breakfast nook, this open floor plan is one to be enjoyed with a wood burning fireplace as the main focal point. The primary bedroom is a true retreat located on the main level providing you with extra privacy. With a full en suite and oversized walk-in closet, this primary offers comfort and functionality. An additional bedroom and en suite can be found on the first floor - perfect for multigenerational living. Upstairs pleasantly surprised with the expansive game room and sizable secondary bedrooms. There is no shortage of space with the downstairs office and formal dining room. The backyard is a dream come true for entertainers, boasting a covered patio and extended wooden deck. This home and backyard make unwinding after a long day effortless. With its convenient location and easy access to some of San Antonio's most noted attractions, this home is a must see. Schedule a showing today to experience the charm and beauty this home holds!
